==English==
===Noun===
'''prepuce''' (''plural'' '''prepuces''')

# {{anatomy}} The retractable fold of tissue covering the tip of the [[penis]]. Nontechnical name: [[foreskin]].  2.  The homologous covering of the clitoris.

